	bool "QSpan PCI"
	depends on !4xx && !CPM2 && 8xx
	select PPC_I8259
	help
	  Say Y here if you have a system based on a Motorola 8xx-series
	  embedded processor with a QSPAN PCI interface, otherwise say N.

